{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":509,"text":"I'd like to tell you about a legal case that I worked on"},{"time":4841,"text":"involving a man named Steve Titus."}]},{"cues":[{"time":8404,"text":"Titus was a restaurant manager."},{"time":11433,"text":"He was 31 years old, he lived in Seattle, Washington,"},{"time":15523,"text":"he was engaged to Gretchen,"},{"time":17418,"text":"about to be married, she was the love of his life."},{"time":20366,"text":"And one night, the couple went out"},{"time":22650,"text":"for a romantic restaurant meal."},{"time":25655,"text":"They were on their way home,"},{"time":27303,"text":"and they were pulled over by a police officer."},{"time":30253,"text":"You see, Titus' car sort of resembled"},{"time":33570,"text":"a car that was driven earlier in the evening"},{"time":37457,"text":"by a man who raped a female hitchhiker,"},{"time":40863,"text":"and Titus kind of resembled that rapist."},{"time":44457,"text":"So the police took a picture of Titus,"},{"time":47035,"text":"they put it in a photo lineup,"},{"time":49802,"text":"they later showed it to the victim,"},{"time":51962,"text":"and she pointed to Titus' photo."},{"time":54122,"text":"She said, \"That one's the closest.\""},{"time":57743,"text":"The police and the prosecution proceeded with a trial,"},{"time":61631,"text":"and when Steve Titus was put on trial for rape,"},{"time":64972,"text":"the rape victim got on the stand"},{"time":67068,"text":"and said, \"I'm absolutely positive that's the man.\""},{"time":71410,"text":"And Titus was convicted."},{"time":74336,"text":"He proclaimed his innocence,"},{"time":76310,"text":"his family screamed at the jury,"},{"time":78892,"text":"his fiancée collapsed on the floor sobbing,"},{"time":81763,"text":"and Titus is taken away to jail."}]},{"cues":[{"time":85158,"text":"So what would you do at this point?"},{"time":88616,"text":"What would you do?"},{"time":90252,"text":"Well, Titus lost complete faith in the legal system,"},{"time":94020,"text":"and yet he got an idea."},{"time":96052,"text":"He called up the local newspaper,"},{"time":98483,"text":"he got the interest of an investigative journalist,"},{"time":101870,"text":"and that journalist actually found the real rapist,"},{"time":106606,"text":"a man who ultimately confessed to this rape,"},{"time":109959,"text":"a man who was thought to have committed 50 rapes"},{"time":113251,"text":"in that area,"},{"time":114583,"text":"and when this information was given to the judge,"},{"time":117757,"text":"the judge set Titus free."}]},{"cues":[{"time":120693,"text":"And really, that's where this case should have ended."},{"time":124724,"text":"It should have been over."},{"time":125847,"text":"Titus should have thought of this as a horrible year,"},{"time":128367,"text":"a year of accusation and trial, but over."}]},{"cues":[{"time":132203,"text":"It didn't end that way."},{"time":134250,"text":"Titus was so bitter."},{"time":136928,"text":"He'd lost his job. He couldn't get it back."},{"time":139508,"text":"He lost his fiancée."},{"time":141351,"text":"She couldn't put up with his persistent anger."},{"time":144257,"text":"He lost his entire savings,"},{"time":146403,"text":"and so he decided to file a lawsuit"},{"time":149261,"text":"against the police and others whom he felt"},{"time":151542,"text":"were responsible for his suffering."}]},{"cues":[{"time":153861,"text":"And that's when I really started working on this case,"},{"time":158574,"text":"trying to figure out"},{"time":160535,"text":"how did that victim go from"},{"time":162609,"text":"\"That one's the closest\""},{"time":164137,"text":"to \"I'm absolutely positive that's the guy.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":168887,"text":"Well, Titus was consumed with his civil case."},{"time":172166,"text":"He spent every waking moment thinking about it,"},{"time":175200,"text":"and just days before he was to have his day in court,"},{"time":179351,"text":"he woke up in the morning,"},{"time":181570,"text":"doubled over in pain,"},{"time":183378,"text":"and died of a stress-related heart attack."},{"time":186072,"text":"He was 35 years old."}]},{"cues":[{"time":189259,"text":"So I was asked to work on Titus' case"},{"time":194069,"text":"because I'm a psychological scientist."},{"time":196584,"text":"I study memory. I've studied memory for decades."},{"time":200411,"text":"And if I meet somebody on an airplane --"},{"time":203800,"text":"this happened on the way over to Scotland --"},{"time":205896,"text":"if I meet somebody on an airplane,"},{"time":207726,"text":"and we ask each other, \"What do you do? What do you do?\""},{"time":210771,"text":"and I say \"I study memory,\""},{"time":212222,"text":"they usually want to tell me how they have trouble remembering names,"},{"time":215602,"text":"or they've got a relative who's got Alzheimer's"},{"time":218416,"text":"or some kind of memory problem,"},{"time":220481,"text":"but I have to tell them"},{"time":222697,"text":"I don't study when people forget."},{"time":226202,"text":"I study the opposite: when they remember,"},{"time":229204,"text":"when they remember things that didn't happen"},{"time":231957,"text":"or remember things that were different"},{"time":233922,"text":"from the way they really were."},{"time":235947,"text":"I study false memories."}]},{"cues":[{"time":240683,"text":"Unhappily, Steve Titus is not the only person"},{"time":244990,"text":"to be convicted based on somebody's false memory."},{"time":249295,"text":"In one project in the United States,"},{"time":252603,"text":"information has been gathered"},{"time":254855,"text":"on 300 innocent people,"},{"time":258789,"text":"300 defendants who were convicted of crimes they didn't do."},{"time":262684,"text":"They spent 10, 20, 30 years in prison for these crimes,"},{"time":267984,"text":"and now DNA testing has proven"},{"time":270411,"text":"that they are actually innocent."},{"time":273327,"text":"And when those cases have been analyzed,"},{"time":275848,"text":"three quarters of them"},{"time":277989,"text":"are due to faulty memory, faulty eyewitness memory."}]},{"cues":[{"time":283600,"text":"Well, why?"},{"time":284863,"text":"Like the jurors who convicted those innocent people"},{"time":288314,"text":"and the jurors who convicted Titus,"},{"time":290598,"text":"many people believe that memory"},{"time":292839,"text":"works like a recording device."},{"time":294486,"text":"You just record the information,"},{"time":296743,"text":"then you call it up and play it back"},{"time":299390,"text":"when you want to answer questions or identify images."},{"time":302817,"text":"But decades of work in psychology"},{"time":304980,"text":"has shown that this just isn't true."},{"time":308133,"text":"Our memories are constructive."},{"time":310563,"text":"They're reconstructive."},{"time":312132,"text":"Memory works a little bit more like a Wikipedia page:"},{"time":315613,"text":"You can go in there and change it, but so can other people."},{"time":320726,"text":"I first started studying this constructive memory process"},{"time":325975,"text":"in the 1970s."},{"time":328390,"text":"I did my experiments that involved showing people"},{"time":332813,"text":"simulated crimes and accidents"},{"time":335318,"text":"and asking them questions about what they remember."},{"time":338836,"text":"In one study, we showed people a simulated accident"},{"time":342775,"text":"and we asked people,"},{"time":344053,"text":"how fast were the cars going when they hit each other?"},{"time":346917,"text":"And we asked other people,"},{"time":348551,"text":"how fast were the cars going when they smashed into each other?"},{"time":352240,"text":"And if we asked the leading \"smashed\" question,"},{"time":355242,"text":"the witnesses told us the cars were going faster,"},{"time":358527,"text":"and moreover, that leading \"smashed\" question"},{"time":362524,"text":"caused people to be more likely to tell us"},{"time":365384,"text":"that they saw broken glass in the accident scene"},{"time":368451,"text":"when there wasn't any broken glass at all."},{"time":372230,"text":"In another study, we showed a simulated accident"},{"time":375119,"text":"where a car went through an intersection with a stop sign,"},{"time":378779,"text":"and if we asked a question that insinuated it was a yield sign,"},{"time":383711,"text":"many witnesses told us they remember seeing a yield sign"},{"time":387560,"text":"at the intersection, not a stop sign."}]},{"cues":[{"time":391017,"text":"And you might be thinking, well, you know,"},{"time":393206,"text":"these are filmed events,"},{"time":394529,"text":"they are not particularly stressful."},{"time":396457,"text":"Would the same kind of mistakes be made"},{"time":399191,"text":"with a really stressful event?"},{"time":402142,"text":"In a study we published just a few months ago,"},{"time":405233,"text":"we have an answer to this question,"},{"time":407537,"text":"because what was unusual about this study"},{"time":410301,"text":"is we arranged for people to have a very stressful experience."},{"time":415933,"text":"The subjects in this study"},{"time":418162,"text":"were members of the U.S. military"},{"time":420672,"text":"who were undergoing a harrowing training exercise"},{"time":425097,"text":"to teach them what it's going to be like for them"},{"time":427879,"text":"if they are ever captured as prisoners of war."},{"time":431797,"text":"And as part of this training exercise,"},{"time":434227,"text":"these soldiers are interrogated in an aggressive,"},{"time":437756,"text":"hostile, physically abusive fashion for 30 minutes"},{"time":442842,"text":"and later on they have to try to identify"},{"time":445659,"text":"the person who conducted that interrogation."},{"time":448682,"text":"And when we feed them suggestive information"},{"time":452505,"text":"that insinuates it's a different person,"},{"time":455283,"text":"many of them misidentify their interrogator,"},{"time":459320,"text":"often identifying someone who doesn't even remotely"},{"time":463155,"text":"resemble the real interrogator."}]},{"cues":[{"time":466259,"text":"And so what these studies are showing"},{"time":468560,"text":"is that when you feed people misinformation"},{"time":472420,"text":"about some experience that they may have had,"},{"time":475800,"text":"you can distort or contaminate or change their memory."}]},{"cues":[{"time":481455,"text":"Well out there in the real world,"},{"time":483655,"text":"misinformation is everywhere."},{"time":486546,"text":"We get misinformation"},{"time":487906,"text":"not only if we're questioned in a leading way,"},{"time":490822,"text":"but if we talk to other witnesses"},{"time":493269,"text":"who might consciously or inadvertently feed us"},{"time":496302,"text":"some erroneous information,"},{"time":498439,"text":"or if we see media coverage about some event we might have experienced,"},{"time":503169,"text":"all of these provide the opportunity"},{"time":505962,"text":"for this kind of contamination of our memory."}]},{"cues":[{"time":510312,"text":"In the 1990s, we began to see"},{"time":514100,"text":"an even more extreme kind of memory problem."},{"time":518783,"text":"Some patients were going into therapy with one problem --"},{"time":521879,"text":"maybe they had depression, an eating disorder --"},{"time":524793,"text":"and they were coming out of therapy"},{"time":527546,"text":"with a different problem."},{"time":530207,"text":"Extreme memories for horrific brutalizations,"},{"time":533908,"text":"sometimes in satanic rituals,"},{"time":535891,"text":"sometimes involving really bizarre and unusual elements."},{"time":540588,"text":"One woman came out of psychotherapy"},{"time":543142,"text":"believing that she'd endured years"},{"time":545570,"text":"of ritualistic abuse, where she was forced into a pregnancy"},{"time":549472,"text":"and that the baby was cut from her belly."},{"time":552038,"text":"But there were no physical scars"},{"time":554397,"text":"or any kind of physical evidence"},{"time":556423,"text":"that could have supported her story."},{"time":559304,"text":"And when I began looking into these cases,"},{"time":562312,"text":"I was wondering,"},{"time":563762,"text":"where do these bizarre memories come from?"},{"time":566090,"text":"And what I found is that most of these situations"},{"time":570477,"text":"involved some particular form of psychotherapy."},{"time":575968,"text":"And so I asked,"},{"time":577567,"text":"were some of the things going on in this psychotherapy --"},{"time":580955,"text":"like the imagination exercises"},{"time":583839,"text":"or dream interpretation,"},{"time":585896,"text":"or in some cases hypnosis,"},{"time":588028,"text":"or in some cases exposure to false information --"},{"time":591846,"text":"were these leading these patients"},{"time":594633,"text":"to develop these very bizarre,"},{"time":597310,"text":"unlikely memories?"},{"time":600241,"text":"And I designed some experiments"},{"time":602400,"text":"to try to study the processes that were being used"},{"time":607425,"text":"in this psychotherapy so I could study"},{"time":610498,"text":"the development of these very rich false memories."}]},{"cues":[{"time":614049,"text":"In one of the first studies we did,"},{"time":616457,"text":"we used suggestion,"},{"time":618810,"text":"a method inspired by the psychotherapy we saw in these cases,"},{"time":622873,"text":"we used this kind of suggestion"},{"time":624983,"text":"and planted a false memory"},{"time":626835,"text":"that when you were a kid, five or six years old,"},{"time":629912,"text":"you were lost in a shopping mall."},{"time":632163,"text":"You were frightened. You were crying."},{"time":634663,"text":"You were ultimately rescued by an elderly person"},{"time":637177,"text":"and reunited with the family."},{"time":639029,"text":"And we succeeded in planting this memory"},{"time":641637,"text":"in the minds of about a quarter of our subjects."},{"time":645743,"text":"And you might be thinking, well,"},{"time":647748,"text":"that's not particularly stressful."},{"time":650094,"text":"But we and other investigators have planted"},{"time":653463,"text":"rich false memories of things that were"},{"time":656221,"text":"much more unusual and much more stressful."},{"time":659136,"text":"So in a study done in Tennessee,"},{"time":661675,"text":"researchers planted the false memory"},{"time":664091,"text":"that when you were a kid, you nearly drowned"},{"time":666665,"text":"and had to be rescued by a life guard."},{"time":669172,"text":"And in a study done in Canada,"},{"time":671475,"text":"researchers planted the false memory"},{"time":673999,"text":"that when you were a kid,"},{"time":675227,"text":"something as awful as being attacked by a vicious animal"},{"time":678957,"text":"happened to you,"},{"time":680339,"text":"succeeding with about half of their subjects."},{"time":683761,"text":"And in a study done in Italy,"},{"time":686113,"text":"researchers planted the false memory,"},{"time":688771,"text":"when you were a kid, you witnessed demonic possession."}]},{"cues":[{"time":693983,"text":"I do want to add that it might seem"},{"time":696190,"text":"like we are traumatizing these experimental subjects"},{"time":699929,"text":"in the name of science,"},{"time":701529,"text":"but our studies have gone through thorough evaluation"},{"time":706167,"text":"by research ethics boards"},{"time":708142,"text":"that have made the decision"},{"time":710484,"text":"that the temporary discomfort that some"},{"time":713557,"text":"of these subjects might experience in these studies"},{"time":716641,"text":"is outweighed by the importance of this problem"},{"time":720541,"text":"for understanding memory processes"},{"time":723648,"text":"and the abuse of memory that is going on"},{"time":726994,"text":"in some places in the world."}]},{"cues":[{"time":730287,"text":"Well, to my surprise,"},{"time":733325,"text":"when I published this work and began to speak out"},{"time":736754,"text":"against this particular brand of psychotherapy,"},{"time":740649,"text":"it created some pretty bad problems for me:"},{"time":744629,"text":"hostilities, primarily from the repressed memory therapists,"},{"time":749530,"text":"who felt under attack,"},{"time":751206,"text":"and by the patients whom they had influenced."},{"time":754734,"text":"I had sometimes armed guards at speeches"},{"time":757671,"text":"that I was invited to give,"},{"time":759576,"text":"people trying to drum up letter-writing campaigns to get me fired."},{"time":763793,"text":"But probably the worst"},{"time":765774,"text":"was I suspected that a woman"},{"time":768541,"text":"was innocent of abuse"},{"time":770965,"text":"that was being claimed by her grown daughter."},{"time":773801,"text":"She accused her mother of sexual abuse"},{"time":777218,"text":"based on a repressed memory."},{"time":779077,"text":"And this accusing daughter had actually allowed her story"},{"time":781960,"text":"to be filmed and presented in public places."},{"time":785394,"text":"I was suspicious of this story,"},{"time":787903,"text":"and so I started to investigate,"},{"time":790203,"text":"and eventually found information that convinced me"},{"time":794686,"text":"that this mother was innocent."},{"time":796975,"text":"I published an exposé on the case,"},{"time":799936,"text":"and a little while later, the accusing daughter"},{"time":803380,"text":"filed a lawsuit."},{"time":804901,"text":"Even though I'd never mentioned her name,"},{"time":807256,"text":"she sued me for defamation and invasion of privacy."},{"time":811618,"text":"And I went through nearly five years"},{"time":814341,"text":"of dealing with this messy, unpleasant litigation,"},{"time":820893,"text":"but finally, finally, it was over and I could really"},{"time":824567,"text":"get back to my work."},{"time":826991,"text":"In the process, however, I became part"},{"time":829476,"text":"of a disturbing trend in America"},{"time":832130,"text":"where scientists are being sued"},{"time":834237,"text":"for simply speaking out on matters of great public controversy."}]},{"cues":[{"time":838836,"text":"When I got back to my work, I asked this question:"},{"time":842194,"text":"if I plant a false memory in your mind,"},{"time":844592,"text":"does it have repercussions?"},{"time":846436,"text":"Does it affect your later thoughts,"},{"time":848395,"text":"your later behaviors?"},{"time":850496,"text":"Our first study planted a false memory"},{"time":852523,"text":"that you got sick as a child eating certain foods:"},{"time":855849,"text":"hard-boiled eggs, dill pickles, strawberry ice cream."},{"time":858848,"text":"And we found that once we planted this false memory,"},{"time":862038,"text":"people didn't want to eat the foods as much"},{"time":864489,"text":"at an outdoor picnic."},{"time":866749,"text":"The false memories aren't necessarily bad or unpleasant."},{"time":870622,"text":"If we planted a warm, fuzzy memory"},{"time":872980,"text":"involving a healthy food like asparagus,"},{"time":876001,"text":"we could get people to want to eat asparagus more."},{"time":879476,"text":"And so what these studies are showing"},{"time":881850,"text":"is that you can plant false memories"},{"time":883965,"text":"and they have repercussions"},{"time":885378,"text":"that affect behavior long after the memories take hold."}]},{"cues":[{"time":890463,"text":"Well, along with this ability"},{"time":892887,"text":"to plant memories and control behavior"},{"time":895810,"text":"obviously come some important ethical issues,"},{"time":899991,"text":"like, when should we use this mind technology?"},{"time":903050,"text":"And should we ever ban its use?"},{"time":906730,"text":"Therapists can't ethically plant false memories"},{"time":909513,"text":"in the mind of their patients"},{"time":911100,"text":"even if it would help the patient,"},{"time":913664,"text":"but there's nothing to stop a parent"},{"time":915286,"text":"from trying this out on their overweight or obese teenager."},{"time":919735,"text":"And when I suggested this publicly,"},{"time":922340,"text":"it created an outcry again."},{"time":925686,"text":"\"There she goes. She's advocating that parents lie to their children.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":929719,"text":"Hello, Santa Claus. (Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":931964,"text":"I mean, another way to think about this is,"},{"time":941461,"text":"which would you rather have,"},{"time":943494,"text":"a kid with obesity, diabetes, shortened lifespan,"},{"time":946523,"text":"all the things that go with it,"},{"time":948055,"text":"or a kid with one little extra bit of false memory?"},{"time":951071,"text":"I know what I would choose for a kid of mine."}]},{"cues":[{"time":954462,"text":"But maybe my work has made me different from most people."},{"time":958439,"text":"Most people cherish their memories,"},{"time":960518,"text":"know that they represent their identity,"},{"time":962672,"text":"who they are, where they came from."},{"time":964697,"text":"And I appreciate that. I feel that way too."},{"time":967555,"text":"But I know from my work"},{"time":969760,"text":"how much fiction is already in there."},{"time":974241,"text":"If I've learned anything from these decades"},{"time":976973,"text":"of working on these problems, it's this:"},{"time":979383,"text":"just because somebody tells you something"},{"time":981594,"text":"and they say it with confidence,"},{"time":983169,"text":"just because they say it with lots of detail,"},{"time":985849,"text":"just because they express emotion when they say it,"},{"time":988608,"text":"it doesn't mean that it really happened."},{"time":991810,"text":"We can't reliably distinguish true memories from false memories."},{"time":995675,"text":"We need independent corroboration."},{"time":999223,"text":"Such a discovery has made me more tolerant"},{"time":1002313,"text":"of the everyday memory mistakes"},{"time":1004452,"text":"that my friends and family members make."},{"time":1007366,"text":"Such a discovery might have saved Steve Titus,"},{"time":1011900,"text":"the man whose whole future was snatched away"},{"time":1015476,"text":"by a false memory."}]},{"cues":[{"time":1017714,"text":"But meanwhile, we should all keep in mind,"},{"time":1020530,"text":"we'd do well to,"},{"time":1022166,"text":"that memory, like liberty,"},{"time":1026037,"text":"is a fragile thing."},{"time":1029731,"text":"Thank you. Thank you."},{"time":1032669,"text":"Thank you. (Applause)"},{"time":1035397,"text":"Thanks very much. (Applause)"}]}]}